
========
OPENMAIL
========


FILES

kvcred.py : implement credentials using a key-value store

kvdomain.py : implements a Mail Domain (for ESMTP delivery) using a key-value store

kvmailbox.py : implements Maildir-semantics using key-value store

riakkv.py : implements basic key-value mail store actions using Riak

pop3server.py : implements a POP3 service using our key-value mailbox

mytap.py : this provides our key-value ESMTP service for the twistd tap infrastructure.

webmail.py : kind of web interface for users, currently can manage their name/password with this.

openmail.tac : this .tac script can be used to start the POP3 service and the web front for users

